&xpdf-time;</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</sect3>
                                                                                
<sect3><title><application>Xpdf</application> dependencies</title>
<sect4><title>Required</title>
<para><xref linkend="xfree86"/> and <xref linkend="lesstif"/>
</para></sect4>
<sect4><title>Optional</title>
<para>Installed fonts: <xref linkend="gs"/>, <xref
linkend="freetype2"/>, t1lib and TrueType</para></sect4>
</sect3>

